     PAGE: SINGLE EMPLOYEE
══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="page" id="page-single">
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>Single Employee Pulse Survey</h2>
    <p>Enter survey responses for one employee to generate a turnover risk prediction and retention strategy recommendations.</p>
