          <tr><td><strong>Working Conditions</strong></td><td>Resource/equipment upgrades; rural/remote location incentives; flexible arrangements</td><td>3.0–3.6</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Safety</strong></td><td>Safety culture training; supervisor accountability; employee well-being programs</td><td>—</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Job Security</strong></td><td>Succession planning; mentorship; knowledge management tools; transparent communication</td><td>3.0–3.3</td></tr>
